msgstr "(At least 2 engineers) Quick, jury-rig them a space ride!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1406
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_ENGINEERS\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"With dubious logic, you get your crew back in through the same breach! But "
"also take some hull damage."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1414
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_ENGINEERS\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM_ANY\"]/text"
msgstr "That was close! Maybe we can go again?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1420
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_ENGINEERS\""
" and not(@lvl)]/text"
msgstr "You do not have enough engineer-class crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1425
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/text"
msgstr "...There's nothing we can do about it, focus on the fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1427
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As your crew is lost alone in the void, the others refuse to ram that ship "
"again!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1432
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "Your clonebay successfully revived your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1436
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "(Mind Control) Obey your captain!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1438
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pre-programmed mind pulse is released and the crew stops complaining. "
"Your methods are unethical but effective."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1440
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM_ANY\"]/text"
msgstr "That's more like it."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1445
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Actually I'm feeling bad about this now, forget it."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1451
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_CREW\"]/choice[13]/event/choice[@req=\"mind\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Some way to control the crew's minds would help us in cases like this..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1497
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_BREACHES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"We tore open our hull on a sharp piece of debris!\n"
"\tThe damage is superficial but the crew is now very afraid of getting spaced through a breach..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1505
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_OWN_OUTCOME_BAD_BREACHES\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "(Shipvore Ram) Maybe we can go again."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1590
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_FP_OWN_OUTCOME_GETHEAL\"]/text"
msgstr "The debris is perfect for quick but extensive repairs!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:1593
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIPVORE_RAM_FP_OWN_OUTCOME_GETHEAL\"]/choice/text"
