msgstr "Choking F.I.N.E. [Cost: 55~, 1}, 1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5889
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_SYSTEM_DJMOD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[@req=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"RK Punk \"Demicloners\": With no Clonebay, your dying crew resurrect as a lesser version (Soldier = default Human, etc.)\n"
"\t\t\tIf none exists, they become Morphs. When Morphs die, nothing happens. Does not work for event deaths. [ALREADY INSTALLED]"

